FT  24 JUN 92 / UK Company News: Hambros Inv net asset value lower
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Hambros Investment Trust, a subsidiary of Hambros, had a net asset value of
46.78p at March 31 compared with 48.6p a year earlier.
Net revenue for the 12 months fell from Pounds 1.35m to Pounds 49,065 after
