family stately home under the thumb of his old nanny. Along comes Gloria
Hepburn, a thrusting American Ms, as business manager. Culture clash.
It is a good night for secret agent freaks. Timewatch is devoted again to a
European terrorist network called Gladio (8.10 BBC2) and BBC1 begins a
six-part series, CIA, about America's Central Intelligence Agency.
